  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn></math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math><mn>5</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>17</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>6</mn></math></p>\n<p>The solution to the given system of equations is <math><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfenced></math>. What is the value of <math><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>y</mi></math>?</p>",
